  "reference_number": "SUD0017",
  "remarks": "\nRed Rock Mining Company is an involved person under the Sudan (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2020 (i) through its association with Sudan Master Technology; and (ii) Red Rock Mining Company is itself responsible for action, policy or activity which threatens the peace, stability and security of Sudan because it has played a central role in funding one of the main parties to the conflict, the Sudanese Armed Forces (SAF).\n",
